            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1704810321254-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1704810321254-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken thighs are browned, add the<strong> coconut stock </strong>and cook for a further 10-12 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce is thickened – this is your <strong>Indonesian-style</strong> <strong>chicken thigh rendang</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1704810322799-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
