        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fluff the<strong> green bean rice </strong>with a fork</p><p>Serve the <strong>Indonesian-style chicken thigh rendang</strong> over the <strong>green bean rice </strong>and garnish with your <strong>remaining chilli flakes</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
